Uses of Package
dooyit.ui

  • Packages that use dooyit.ui 
    Package Description
    dooyit.ui  
  • Classes in dooyit.ui used by dooyit.ui 
    Class and Description
    UICategoryBox
    The UICategoryBox class contains the methods to create and retrieve a category menu button.
    UICategoryBoxContainer
    The UICategoryBoxContainer class contains the methods to create and retrieve a list of UICategoryBox objects.
    UICommandBox
    The UICommandBox class contains the methods to modify the textfield in which the user types his commands, as well as to retrieve the user's command input history.
    UIController
    The UIController class contains methods to initialize all other classes belonging to the UI.
    UIDayBox
    The UIDayBox class contains all the UITaskBox objects whose Task belongs to a single day or Task type.
    UIDayBoxContainer
    The UIDayBoxContainer class contains the methods to initialize UIDayBox and update their views.
    UIHeader
    The UIHeader class contains methods to initialize the header view of the UI.
    UIHelpBox
    The UIHelpBox class contains the methods to initialize the help box, control its visibility and set the message to be displayed.
    UIMainViewType
    The UIMainViewtype class contains the enumerated types of the UI's main view.
    UIMessageBox
    The UIMessageBox class contains the methods to initialize the message box, control its visibility and set its displayed message.
    UIMessageType
    The UIMessageType class contains the enumerated types of messages that are displayed in the message box.
    UISideMenu
    The UISideMenu class contains the methods to initialize the side menu and update its menu buttons.
    UITaskBox
    The UITaskBox class contains the methods to initialize a task view and change its layout and dimensions.
    UITheme
    The UITheme class contains the enumerated types for the applicaton's skins.
